title: The Start of the Pentagon's Secret UFO Project - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 12/21/17

description:
George Noory and investigative TV journalist George Knapp, a weekend host of Coast to Coast, discuss his interview with former Nevada Senator Harry Reid, who was instrumental is setting up the recently disclosed Pentagon program looking into the proof of UFOs and aliens.
